data.description: Welcome to this lovely home situated less than 1 mile from Indian Hills Golf Course & 10 minutes to Greers Ferry Lake. This property offers easy access to outdoor recreational activities for golf enthusiasts. As you enter the home, you will immediately notice the inviting deck, providing a perfect spot to relax & enjoy the natural beauty of the area. The property has been thoughtfully designed to be handicap accessible, ensuring comfortable living for individuals with special needs. Both the bathrooms & the kitchen have been recently updated, showcasing modern finishes & fixtures. The kitchen boasts ample counter space & storage, making it a chef's dream.  A sunroom/office adds additional living space & can be utilized for various purposes. The highlight of the living room is a beautiful stone fireplace, creating a cozy atmosphere during colder months. The yard features stunning landscaping, enhancing the overall appeal of the property. The presence of a common area behind the home adds an extra element of privacy, allowing for peaceful & tranquil living. The garage has been completely redone in recent years, providing a well-maintained space for your vehicle. See agent remarks.
